your birthday. I have some ideas.

767
00:45:17,616 --> 00:45:19,550
<i>Yeah? Okay.</i>

768
00:45:33,049 --> 00:45:34,716
Alex called.

769
00:45:35,215 --> 00:45:36,680
Is she okay?

770
00:45:36,682 --> 00:45:39,081
Well, she will be.

771
00:45:39,083 --> 00:45:40,651
It's about a boy.

772
00:45:41,948 --> 00:45:44,214
(SIGHS) I don't have all the answers,

773
00:45:44,216 --> 00:45:48,114
but I try to slip her a
little advice when she lets me.

774
00:45:48,116 --> 00:45:50,815
I have a feeling you have a lot of answers.

775
00:45:53,382 --> 00:45:55,983
See? Wild watercress. I just found it.

776
00:45:56,815 --> 00:45:57,816
Hmm.

777
00:45:58,916 --> 00:46:01,947
Mmm. It's perfect, not hot and peppery

778
00:46:01,949 --> 00:46:03,947
