984
00:57:48,248 --> 00:57:51,346
MARTINE: They put some salt
and get rid of all this bile.

985
00:57:51,348 --> 00:57:54,946
JACQUES: You need to purge the
snails before you cook them.

986
00:57:54,948 --> 00:57:58,212
They have to empty the intestines.

987
00:57:58,214 --> 00:58:00,212
(SPEAKING FRENCH)

988
00:58:00,214 --> 00:58:03,680
This is a roasted cock from Bresse, yes?

989
00:58:03,682 --> 00:58:05,613
- And usually it has blue feet.
- Ha!

990
00:58:05,615 --> 00:58:07,279
This is the best in France.

991
00:58:07,281 --> 00:58:08,613
Yes, and look...

992
00:58:08,615 --> 00:58:10,079
They serve the breast first

993
00:58:10,081 --> 00:58:13,045
