00:58:59,682 --> 00:59:01,312
No, no, please, we're going to Paris.

1007
00:59:01,314 --> 00:59:03,613
Please don't give him any ideas.

1008
00:59:03,615 --> 00:59:06,213
Jacques, this has to be our last stop.

1009
00:59:06,215 --> 00:59:07,779
- Okay?
- JACQUES: All right.

